OL,3,CTata boss '100% committed' to building
OL,4,Celectric arc at Port Talbot plant
OL,6,FThe boss of Tata Steel has said he is
OL,7,F"100% committed to building an
OL,8,Felectric arc" at the Port Talbot site
OL,9,Fafter a "very difficult day" for those
OL,10,Fwhose jobs are at risk.
OL,12,FThachat Viswanath Narendran told ITV
OL,13,FWales he "fully empathises" with those
OL,14,Fimpacted by the company's decision to
OL,15,Fshut down its blast furnaces at the
OL,16,Fsouth Wales site, putting nearly 3,000
OL,17,Fjobs at risk UK-wide.
OL,19,FHe said he was committed to building
OL,20,Fan electric arc so that the business
OL,21,Fis "not always at the edge of a cliff".
